                  </div>
                  <span class="">最后一幕果然是最好看的，一步步把剧情推向高潮，看得我难受！</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-05 18:27</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44607142-1.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">鸠占鹊巢，理直气壮。</div></div></div><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44607142-3.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">坚持的人，都活得不好，但没有这些坚持的人，国家绝对不会好。</div></div></div><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44607142-6.jpg"></div></div><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44607142-2.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">活死人一般，生不如死不过如此，在这个年代，或许活着就是死了。</div></div></div><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44607142-4.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">要多可笑，有多可笑。活着就是恶心，站如同跪，立如同弯。不说人话，只管中西合璧，不西不中不洋不华，何身为人，不如为畜，除了“hao”还能叫出点别的声调，若为狗，还能浅通人性！</div></div></div><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44607142-5.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">坚持的人，死了。变通的人，死了。这种丧尽天良，辱没三观的年代，什么人都得死。</div></div></div><p>最后一幕果然是最好看的，一步步把剧情推向高潮，看得我难受！</p>
